CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "More Teachers And Attendant To Senior Queen - ...Right photo: Norrine West Lyons and Ernestine Gloster Parks were granted degrees of Master of Education. ..in the Pittsburgh school system. All are from Pitt."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh Masters of Education graduates Norrine West Lyons and Ernestine Gloster Parks, standing in Syria Mosque, Oakland
